data.description: Come and see this cute ranch featuring three bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and finished basement.  Interior is highlighted by new carpeting and freshly painted.  Kitchen has all appliances included with ample eating area and fan w/built-in dimmer lighting.  Large finished basement allows for numerous functions and is highlighted by adjacent full bathroom.  Entire basement has been perma sealed to prevent water leakage and even guarded with battery backup sump pump system.  Home features a large storage attic and functional utility room.  Enjoy the large yard and get the 16 X 32 kayak pool ready for summer and grill on the patio.  Convenient parking is provided with long driveway and 20 X 20 detached block concrete two car garage.  Home sits on a large half acre yard and has tons of privacy at the end of the street.
